description.V: *mumbling* What? Who knows what? I know what does, but he dozed unwisely! The Hermit of Awadji knows what's what, but what's left of him is I don't know where. But I do know what the Great Fire Djinn enjoys for lunch...mushroom kebabs! Aahahaha!

minidescription.V: Rescue the Hermit of Awadji from the Caverns of Living Fire. But be wary! He is being held captive by a Great Fire Djinn on Level 30.

completiondescription.V: Thanks to you Awadji has returned along with some of my sanity, but please give him time to recover from the ordeal. Upon returning from your next dungeon expedition, seek him near the obelisk.

incompletedescription.V: Erble Gerble What? I see no Awadji!

description.V: Level 2 of The Caverns of Living Fire has become infested with Snakes! If you can kill 4 of them, I'll compensate you fairly....

completiondescription.V:
Thank you for clearing out that infestation for me! Here is your reward!
You receive 288 Experience 140 Fame 1464 Gold

incompletedescription.V: Please return when all of the Snakes have been killed.

description.V: I've always wanted a fine Demonchewer's Soft Gloves of the Hare, but I just don't trust these shifty merchants. I've heard you can find all sorts of things in the dungeons - especially on level 2 of The Caverns of Living Fire. If you run across one, I'd be happy to buy it from you!

minidescription.V: Retrieve Demonchewer's Soft Gloves of the Hare from level 2.

completiondescription.V:
Thank goodness! You've found the Demonchewer's Soft Gloves of the Hare! And here is your reward. My thanks to you!
You receive 371 Experience 142 Fame 1741 Gold

incompletedescription.V: Please return when you have found the Demonchewer's Soft Gloves of the Hare.

name.V: Demonchewer's Soft Gloves of the Hare

description.V: A Daorthak's Amethyst Stud of Life that has been in my family for centuries has been stolen! I've heard that a Mantoid named Swordgrinder has it, and that he roams the 2nd level of The Caverns of Living Fire. Please retrieve it for me!

minidescription.V: Destroy Swordgrinder the Mantoid on level 2 and retrieve Daorthak's Amethyst Stud of Life.

completiondescription.V:
Ah! You've found the Daorthak's Amethyst Stud of Life! And here is your reward. My thanks to you!
You receive 869 Experience 138 Fame 2305 Gold

incompletedescription.V: Please return when you have found the Daorthak's Amethyst Stud of Life.

description.V: Yesterday, I sat upon a gilded throne, ruling all that you see as the mighty king of Ekbatan. I speak to you now as nothing more than a lowly beggar. You must lift this curse... if not for me, then for my kingdom. Redeem yourself, and restore our glorious city!

incompletedescription.V: Please return when the task is complete!

name.V: Wighteater's Healthy Initiate's Cowl of the Tortoise
